/r38SBpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr38SBpm.jpg&h=3677182c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSINOMAX超<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">致敏</span></strong>💥😱<br />\n價值數千元床褥💰<br />\n試睡💤即<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">出紅疹</span></strong>😷<br />\n更有人紅腫流膿😭<br />\n搵TVB偽人代言，黑🖤保證<br />\n<br />\n替代選擇：Casablanca (用viutv藝人)<br />\n<br />\n[Source]<br />\n致敏出疹、流膿 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RHTLTP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RHTLTP&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ca7c8d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2RHTLTP</a><br />\n<br />\n#陳豪 #SINOMAX<br />\n<br />\n※留言template<br />\n<blockquote>抵制TVB運動已開始半年，貴公司仍然用無綫電視藝人作代言實屬不智，本人深表遺憾，並呼籲貴公司停止與無綫藝人合作，否則將永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幾幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wnC79Lp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwnC79Lp.jpg&h=68b5885d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbfJH5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbfJH5p.jpg&h=52cb803c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DnzPLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DnzPLq.png&h=3aa51acd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">記得bookmark<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</span></strong><br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?